The dataset was analyzed to check its structure, missing values, duplicates, and statistical summary. 
Missing values were handled by filling numerical columns with the median and categorical columns with the mode. 
Duplicate records were removed to improve data quality. Outliers were treated using the IQR method to reduce the impact of extreme values. 
Categorical variables were encoded using one-hot encoding, and numerical features were scaled using StandardScaler. 
The dataset is now clean and ready for machine learning.
